snippet.title: Bionic Bay - New Release Date Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
In this trailer, get another peek into the atmospheric sci-fi world of Bionic Bay. It showcases its intricate pixel art, physics-based mechanics, sweat-inducing platforming challenges, and the latest online mode feature; and unveils a new release date.
Bionic Bay will be hopping onto Steam and PS5 platforms on 17th April 2025. Wishlist now:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1928690/Bionic_Bay/
PS5: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10011377
